{"tid":2070353,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[twitter支援］被問及BLM Dominic  Raab 表示只會向英女皇及老婆下跪 被左膠圍插","createTime":"2020-06-19T05:30:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T04:27:07.000Z","uid":48083,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"32074d242cb7f1d6b0dba06568e191ca6dd8c68d","tid":2070353,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T05:30:03.000Z","msg":"Goodbye HK, Hello UK<br />\n齊來學英文：你會唔會跪？<br />\n（呢個世代講真話係會被圍插嘅）<br />\n<br />\n今日外交大臣Dominic Raab接受電台訪問，主持問佢會唔會好似某啲美國人咁單膝跪去支持Black Lives Matter。佢話只會向兩個人下跪，英女皇同埋當年求婚嗰個Mrs.，原因亦好簡單：<br />\n<br />\n//&quot;...feels to me like a symbol of subjugation and subordination rather than one of liberation and emancipation.//<br />\n（對我黎講，跪低係一個屈服同從屬多過解放（女權或者黑人）嘅象徵，咁當然每個人嘅感覺唔同，有係個人選擇黎嘅。）<br />\n<br />\n結果就被左膠圍插，老老實實，佢講錯啲咩呢？<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 頂住呀，跟埋香港單嘢先好落台...<br />\n<br />\n#學生字<br />\n<br />\nVideo Source：talkRadio<br />\n原片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/talkradio/status/1273525908465426432?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftalkradio%2Fstatus%2F1273525908465426432%3Fs%3D21&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C%2Fkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=5f8ac939\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftalkradio%2Fstatus%2F1273525908465426432%3Fs%3D21&h=31b5d50a\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/talkradio/status/1273525908465426432?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\nTwitter俾左癌狙擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/DominicRaab\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDominicRaab&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C%2Fkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=23cf88ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/DominicRaab</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/goodbyehkhellouk/videos/272003647384065/?refsrc=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fgoodbyehkhellouk%2Fvideos%2F272003647384065%2F&amp;_rdr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fgoodbyehkhellouk%2Fvideos%2F272003647384065%2F%3Frefsrc%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fm.facebook.com%252Fgoodbyehkhellouk%252Fvideos%252F272003647384065%252F%26_rdr&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C%2Fkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=cf3303bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/goodbyehkhellouk/videos/272003647384065/?refsrc=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fgoodbyehkhellouk%2Fvideos%2F272003647384065%2F&amp;_rdr</a>"},{"pid":"b4864651c174a16d24bef75c63fa058b51932fb4","tid":2070353,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T05:30:50.000Z","msg":"另外：<br />\n<br />\nGoodbye HK, Hello UK<br />\n英國幾有歷史責任甚至係世紀罪人也好，有時候諗嘢係咪要顧慮下對方嘅承受能力呢？<br />\n<br />\n其實呢，外交大臣6月2號响下議院答過一個咁嘅提問（本人睇咗四至五次，呢條係其中一條好多人忽略嘅一條），提問嘅係自由民主黨嘅Wendy Chamberlain，關於好多人所謂嘅平權法案（Hong Kong Bill）：<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Will he consider the proposal made by my right hon. Friend the Member for Orkney and Shetland (Mr Carmichael) in his Hong Kong Bill, which I sponsored, which would offer a pathway to citizenship for ALL Hong Kong citizens.&quot;<br />\n（請問外交大臣會唔會支持之前有議員提交給「香港法案」，即係制定一套特別移民政策比所有香港人（留意係所有），等佢地最後得到英國公民身份？）<br />\n<br />\n可能因為係對面政黨議員提問，而且偏離議題，所以當日外交大臣Dominic Raab係答得特別串嘅：<br />\n<br />\n&quot;We need to be realistic about the volume of people that we in this country could credibly and responsibly absorb. I do not think we can have this debate without acknowledging that.&quot;<br />\n（其實我哋需要面對一個客觀現實，就係呢個國家實際可以正常有效咁，吸納幾多人口。如果對呢個數字係冇概念嘅話，我唔覺得呢件可以討論。）<br />\n<br />\n&quot;The fact is, though, that we have an historic set of responsibilities, as I set out earlier, and we will live up to them.&quot;<br />\n（事實上，我地（對香港）係有歷史責任，正如我之前所講，我地而家就係去承擔呢個責任。）<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 英國政府唔係我開嘅，只不過係分享現實發生咗嘅事，不多不少。將香港人集體變成恩客咁，係咪有點那個呢？"},{"pid":"c306177a87733398a5fcc65f29236fee738ac618","tid":2070353,"uid":28765,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T05:32:58.000Z"